{"tid":1634654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(苦主入)德福商場製造白色恐怖 消費者權益何在","createTime":"2019-10-07T09:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:16:07.000Z","uid":300816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7eca4f26789c3276c507b1c2014d7393aefc25","tid":1634654,"uid":300816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"P牌第一次出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說德福已經好多日因為&ldquo;公眾活動&rdquo;而唔開舖<br />\n但係其實由頭到尾都無事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n渣哥都依然開全日無問題<br />\n但係旗下唔少商戶居然陪地鐵一齊製造白色恐怖 等市民覺得香港真係好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其中一個club house已經連續幾日無開<br />\n打電話去查詢係咩原因唔開 就係覆係地鐵<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">強制關閉</span></strong> 但係消費者已經pre pay晒錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家錢又唔退 sorry又無 <br />\n仲講大話話因為商場全面封閉又無地鐵所以無辦法開門 (係人都知尋日巴士不知幾多)<br />\n有無人都係苦主?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要一齊比地鐵知道佢亂唔做生意係唔得架!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae46f2eb09473df38643c20ad26783a831cbe5b7","tid":1634654,"uid":317625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"商場唱下歌囉"}]}